{"data":[{"date":"15:21 09/08","title":"T\u00e2n binh Barca s\u1eafp chia tay v\u1ee3","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/tan-binh-barca-sap-chia-tay-vo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arturo Vidal th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1eabn hay t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o r\u1eb1ng ph\u00eda sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a anh c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a t\u1edbi hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef l\u00e0 m\u1eb9 v\u00e0 v\u1ee3. Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd th\u00ec b\u00e2n binh Barcelona n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n m\u1eb9 \u0111\u1ec3 chia s\u1ebb. V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u01a1m ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0nh, canh ch\u1eb3ng ng\u1ecdt.</h2><h2>V\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Vidal chia t\u00e1ch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a t\u1edd Marca ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Vidal \u0111ang b\u00ean mi\u1ec7ng v\u1ef1c. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 31 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile v\u00e0 c\u00f4 v\u1ee3 Maria Teresa Matus \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n chung s\u1ed1ng v\u1edbi nhau n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTin \u0111\u1ed3n \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf. Th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u00ec m\u1ed7i khi c\u00e1c t\u00e2n binh ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u h\u00e3nh di\u1ec7n d\u1eabn theo ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00e2n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 v\u1ee3 con. V\u1eady m\u00e0 khi Vidal tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng Barcelona, kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 th\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng Maria Teresa \u0111\u00e2u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n c\u1ecf Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Vidal chia tay v\u1ee3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u00e2n c\u1ecf Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Vidal chia tay v\u1ee3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/vidal2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Gia \u0111\u00ecnh Vidal th\u1eddi c\u00f2n m\u1eb7n n\u1ed3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Instagram c\u1ee7a Vidal c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd anh ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n khoe \u1ea3nh c\u00e1c con. Ch\u1ee9 Vidal kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n khoe \u1ea3nh c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Maria Teresa nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 v\u00ec sao v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Vidal l\u1ea1i c\u01a1m ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0nh, canh ch\u1eb3ng ng\u1ecdt nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u1ec9 th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y Maria Teresa v\u00e0 Vidal g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 ly th\u00e2n. D\u00f9 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o th\u00ec th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c fan kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ecfi ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVidal v\u00e0 Maria Teresa \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi nhau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f2n 10 n\u0103m. Ch\u00e0ng quen n\u00e0ng t\u1eeb h\u1ed3i 2008. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f3 Vidal c\u00f2n \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Leverkusen. Maria Teresa th\u00ec b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u1ea7m l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eabu, cho d\u00f9 c\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 d\u00ednh d\u00e1ng t\u1edbi l\u00e0ng th\u1eddi trang. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 v\u00ec ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1eb9p b\u1eb1ng tu\u1ed5i v\u1edbi Vidal n\u00e0y s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t si\u00eau m\u1eabu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m 2009, Vidal c\u01b0\u1edbi Maria Teresa. C\u00f4 theo anh phi\u00eau l\u01b0u chinh chi\u1ebfn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, t\u1eeb Leverkusen sang Juventus r\u1ed3i tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1edbi Bayern. Maria Teresa \u0111\u00e3 sinh h\u1ea1 cho Vidal ba\u00a0 thi\u00ean th\u1ea7n nh\u1ecf g\u1ed3m Alonso, Elisabetta v\u00e0 Emiliano. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd Vidal \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb Bayern sang Barca, nh\u01b0ng Maria Teresa th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n theo anh. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng fan hi\u1ebfu k\u1ef3 th\u00eam t\u00f2 m\u00f2. H\u1ecd t\u00f2 m\u00f2 ch\u1edd xem Vidal s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ea5m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Barca. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng t\u00f2 m\u00f2 ki\u1ec3m ch\u1ee9ng xem chuy\u1ec7n c\u01a1m ch\u1eb3ng l\u00e0nh, canh ch\u1eb3ng ng\u1ecdt c\u1ee7a v\u1ee3 ch\u1ed3ng Vidal th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<h2>\u0110\u00e1 b\u00f3ng gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00e1o hi\u1ebfu m\u1eb9</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef ph\u00eda sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vidal gi\u1edd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n Maria Teresa. Song anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ee5 n\u1eef \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 coi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap anh n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ngh\u1ec9 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n b\u00f3ng. \u0110\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 th\u00e2n m\u1eabu Jacqueline Pardo c\u1ee7a anh. Vidal t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 r\u1eb1ng nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n quan tr\u1ecdng khi\u1ebfn anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng l\u00e0 v\u00ec m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVidal ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u: \u201cK\u00fd \u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n trong \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i m\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n t\u00f4i nh\u1edb v\u1ec1 th\u1eddi th\u01a1 \u1ea5u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n \u0111\u00f3i v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1n l\u1ea1nh m\u00e0 t\u00f4i v\u00e0 gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean chuy\u1ec7n m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i t\u1ea7n t\u1ea3o khuya s\u1edbm th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ec1n trang tr\u1ea3i cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u00f4i nh\u1edb nh\u01b0 in h\u1ed3i \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edbi 14 tu\u1ed5i. M\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n m\u1eb9 t\u00f4i \u0111i l\u00e0m v\u1ec1 r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed9n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u00e0 l\u1ea3 \u0111i. B\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ec7t s\u1ee9c. T\u00f4i t\u1ef1 nh\u1ee7 l\u00f2ng m\u00ecnh r\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf m\u00e3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ki\u1ebfm ti\u1ec1n gi\u00fap m\u1eb9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ed7i l\u1ea7n ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh lam l\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u1eb9, t\u00f4i l\u1ea1i t\u1ef1 nh\u1ee7 ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c g\u1ea5p ba, g\u1ea5p b\u1ed1n th\u1eadm ch\u00ed g\u1ea5p m\u01b0\u1eddi l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp. K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 sau n\u00e0y khi t\u00f4i th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p r\u1ed3i, nh\u1eefng k\u00fd \u1ee9c \u1ea5y v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng th\u00f4i th\u00fac t\u00f4i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eebng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3i qua tu\u1ed5i th\u01a1 c\u01a1 c\u1ef1c, Vidal t\u1ef1 giao nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 cho m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c con ph\u1ea3i kh\u1ed5 nh\u01b0 anh ng\u00e0y x\u01b0a. Gi\u1edd anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 cho 3 \u0111\u1ee9a con nh\u1ecf \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7y. Ch\u1ec9 ch\u01b0a tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n khi gi\u1edd \u0111ang r\u1ed9 tin \u0111\u1ed3n m\u1eb9 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c con anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n chung nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi anh.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5295","checkdouble":"194112"},{"date":"15:19 09/08","title":"Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/27/ronaldo-thuc-giuc-nguoi-ban-than-marcelo-den-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft \u1edf Real, Marcelo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus.</h2><h2>Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c Marcelo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c Marcelo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c Marcelo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/2/Ronaldo-thuc-giuc-Marcelo-den-Juventus--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Ronaldo mu\u1ed1n Marcelo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed l\u00ean t\u1edbi 105 tri\u1ec7u euro. Song c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 CR7 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u00ecnh &lsquo;c\u01a1 \u0111\u01a1n&rsquo; t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o n\u00e0y \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Real kh\u00e1c s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo&nbsp;Tuttosport, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Marcelo \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chinh chi\u1ebfn c\u00f9ng m\u00ecnh. Ronaldo v\u00e0 Marcelo l\u00e0 c\u1eb7p b\u00e0i tr\u00f9ng \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi nhau \u1edf c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Real su\u1ed1t 9 n\u0103m qua. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1eddi.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, Marcelo c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi Ronaldo, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Brazil v\u1eabn \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf t\u1ea1i Bernabeu. N\u1ebfu Marcelo ra \u0111i, Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00ecm s\u00e2u v\u00e0o kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV&nbsp;Zinedine Zidane v\u00e0 Ronaldo.&nbsp;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u00ed do \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia ch\u01b0a t\u00ednh t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Serie A c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 c\u1ea7n Marcelo. Theo b\u00e1o gi\u1edbi Italia, Juventus ch\u1ec9 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd b\u00e1n Alex Sandro - ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c PSG quan t\u00e2m. Sandro \u0111ang l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Juventus v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 46 tri\u1ec7u \u0111\u00f4la. Do \u0111\u00f3 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Juve mua Marcelo g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra trong h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1c, CLB Real Madrid \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 &nbsp;Miralem Pjanic c\u1ee7a Juve. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00ed t\u01b0\u1edfng cho Luka Modric trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Pjanic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5294","checkdouble":"194109"},{"date":"12:31 09/08","title":"X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n.</h2><h2>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u1eafm gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u1eafm gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u1eafm gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/8/Van-Quyet-nam-giu-bang-thu-quan-cua-DT-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1eafm gi\u1eef t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam&nbsp;</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y sau khi VFF c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD, g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u1eafm gi\u1eef b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m gi\u1eef chi\u1ebfc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong bu\u1ed5i b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn ra m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 hai \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 cho Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o s\u00e1ng nay 9/8. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i ph\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 L\u01b0\u01a1ng Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng (HAGL) v\u00e0 trung v\u1ec7 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng (CLB Viettel).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch t\u1eeb c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1ea1ng v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u00edn nhi\u1ec7m, tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cho th\u1ea5y V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Vinaphone Cup v\u1eeba qua, do \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 s\u1ef1 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u nay (9/8), Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean s\u00e2n G\u00f2 \u0110\u1eadu (B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng) l\u00fac 15h45. \u0110\u1ed9i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u mai 10/9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00e0m th\u1ee7 t\u1ee5c l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 11 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"ASIAD\" title=\"ASIAD\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/CHINH-THUC-HLV-Park-Hang-Seo-loai-Van-Lam-khoi-danh-sach-chinh-thuc-Olympic-Viet-Nam-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Danh s\u00e1ch \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018<span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-thuyen-truong-thai-lan-danh-gia-ve-co-hoi-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194093.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/cuu-thuyen-truong-thai-lan-danh-gia-ve-co-hoi-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-thuyen-truong-thai-lan-danh-gia-ve-co-hoi-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194093.html\">C\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Vinaphone Cup, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u00e1i Lan, \u00f4ng Steve Darby \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu-168-194086.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu-168-194086.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu</span><br>\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;&#10;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5293","checkdouble":"194101"},{"date":"15:42 09/08","title":"B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>T\u1edd b\u00e1o Bola c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</h2><h2>B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 tham d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 Uzbekistan, Palestine v\u00e0 Oman \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao trong m\u1eaft gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u1edd b\u00e1o Bola c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo. Trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y, t\u1edd Bola cho r\u1eb1ng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm khi s\u1edf h\u1eefu th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng t\u1eebng t\u1ea1o d\u1ea5u m\u1ed1c l\u1ecbch s\u1eed khi l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/photo-1-15337765426941939351668.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>T\u1edd b\u00e1o Indonesia n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd b\u00e1o n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 cho bi\u1ebft 12 trong s\u1ed1 20 c\u00e1i t\u00ean d\u1ef1 ASIAD t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 \"2 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o s\u1eafc b\u00e9n l\u00e0 Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi g\u1ecdi danh s\u00e1ch 20 ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u00e0y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 v\u00e0ng, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00e0y d\u1eb7n tr\u1eadn m\u1ea1c. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Bola c\u00f2n kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \"Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u00e2y ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam n\u1eb1m \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, Nepal v\u00e0 Pakistan.\u00a0V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt ch\u1ec9 c\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i U21 tham d\u1ef1, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo c\u1ea1nh tranh ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u, qua \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ea1i l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-194101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.png\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-194101.html\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br />\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-thuyen-truong-thai-lan-danh-gia-ve-co-hoi-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194093.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/cuu-thuyen-truong-thai-lan-danh-gia-ve-co-hoi-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cuu-thuyen-truong-thai-lan-danh-gia-ve-co-hoi-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-168-194093.html\">C\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD</span><br />\r\nCh\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu Vinaphone Cup, c\u1ef1u thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Th\u00e1i Lan, \u00f4ng Steve Darby \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n v\u1ec1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu-168-194086.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu.JPG\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-han-quoc-noi-gi-sau-khi-u23-viet-nam-vo-dich-giai-giao-huu-168-194086.html\">HLV H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu</span><br />\r\nNh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn h\u1ecd l\u00ean ng\u00f4i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5292","checkdouble":"194114"},{"date":"17:08 09/08","title":"\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, ch\u1ecdn B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/7/day-co-phai-ly-do-khien-hlv-park-hang-seo-loai-van-lam-chon-bui-tien-dung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 do ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m chuy\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 InStat th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e3 cho th\u1ea5y th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng l\u1ea1i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi \u2018ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n anh\u2019 \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m.</h2><h2>HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m do Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau khi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu U23 qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf c\u00fap Vinaphone 2018, VFF \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c 20 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Indonesia d\u1ef1 ASIAD.</p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam hi\u1ec7n nay.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, ch\u1ecdn B\u00f9i  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo lo\u1ea1i V\u0103n L\u00e2m, ch\u1ecdn B\u00f9i  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/Dang-Van-Lam-bi-loai-khoi-Asiad-2018-Bat-ngo-nhung-hop-ly-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>V\u0103n L\u00e2m c\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9m h\u1eb3n B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1edf d\u0129 V\u0103n L\u00e2m b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i do HLV Park Hang Seo c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 ASIAD cho Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean n\u1ebfu nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 InStat (ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m chuy\u00ean cung c\u1ea5p th\u00f4ng tin, s\u1ed1 li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7), ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00fd do ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u00f4ng Park \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, theo\u00a0ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m InStat c\u1eadp nh\u1eadp ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 193, c\u00f2n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m ch\u1ec9 \u1edf m\u1ee9c 187. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 trung b\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a n\u0103m 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu t\u00ednh ri\u00eang ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng v\u1eeba qua, ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 c\u1ee7a B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng c\u0169ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa so v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. \u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 243 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Oman, c\u00f2n v\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, con s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 179 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc U23 Palestine.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1 InStat c\u1ee7a V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng v\u1eeba qua ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o n\u00f3i l\u00ean s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin cho Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u1edf ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m, vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chuy\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. N\u1ebfu th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ed1t, anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf AFF Cup v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m nay hay xa h\u01a1n l\u00e0 t\u1ea1i VCK Asian Cup 2019.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 13pt; line-height: 115%; letter-spacing: -0.25pt;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/bao-indonesia-danh-gia-cao-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-168-194114.html\">B\u00e1o Indonesia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br>\r\nT\u1edd b\u00e1o Bola c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ASIAD 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-194101.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/xac-dinh-thu-quan-moi-cua-dt-olympic-viet-nam-tai-asiad-2018-168-194101.html\">X\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018</span><br>\r\nTheo m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u1ea5m b\u0103ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5291","checkdouble":"194122"},{"date":"16:40 09/08","title":"Real n\u00edu k\u00e9o Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o c\u1ee7a Inter","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/real-madrid-muon-giu-chan-luka-modric.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Luka Modric. Inter Milan \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n anh b\u1eb1ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Inter mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Modric</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Champions League sau 6 n\u0103m, Inter Milan quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. M\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u01b0 Radja Nainggolan, Sime Vrsaljko hay Stefan de Vrij\u2026 Ch\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, Inter c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n \u201ccu\u1ed7m\u201d Modric c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n1 n\u0103m tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, d\u00f9 \u1edf tu\u1ed5i 32, Modric v\u1eabn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Anh l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Real \u0111\u0103ng quang ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League m\u00f9a th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ef1u sao Tottenham ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0110T Croatia gi\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Luka Modric h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/real-madrid-muon-giu-chan-luka-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Luka Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, Modric \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh gi\u1ea3i Qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng v\u00e0ng (C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t). \u1ea4n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Modric, Inter v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Croatia nh\u01b0 Brozovic, Perisic hay Vrsaljko ra s\u1ee9c k\u00eau g\u1ecdi anh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ea3 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Inter, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Luka Modric. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3i ng\u1ed9 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n d\u00e0nh cho tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t 6 n\u0103m qua. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez c\u1ee7a Real c\u0169ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 Modric ra \u0111i v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u00edt h\u01a1n 750 tri\u1ec7u Euro, b\u1eb1ng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-ra-gia-modric-cho-cac-doi-tac-180-192606.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/real-ra-gia-modric-cho-cac-doi-tac.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-ra-gia-modric-cho-cac-doi-tac-180-192606.html\">V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, M.U v\u00e0 Inter c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mang Modric r\u1eddi Real</span><br>\r\n<span>Real ra gi\u00e1 Modric cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. Theo \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Croatia, nh\u1eefng Man United hay Inter Milan s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 750...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Modric \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 suy ngh\u0129. Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi Real t\u1edbi Juventus t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi. Gi\u00e1 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng CR7 l\u00e0 1 t\u1ef7 Euro song tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Los Blancos bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u00e1n anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u Euro. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u00f3 l\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Modric hay kh\u00f4ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, Perez t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn. Real m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea d\u01b0\u1edbi d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t th\u00eam nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real tr\u00ean trang bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-thuong-vu-courtois-toi-real-madrid-172-194113.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Courtois t\u1edbi Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chuyen-nhuong-real-madrid-hot-nhat-ngay-0908-180-194097.html\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Real Madrid hot nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y 09/08</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/keylor-navas-phat-bieu-ve-tuong-lai-tai-real-madrid-180-194072.html\">Sao b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t s\u1ee7ng c\u1ee7a Real th\u1ec1 ch\u1ebft \u201cchi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u\u201d c\u00f9ng Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Real</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-thu-mon-courtois-180-194067.html\">Real Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5290","checkdouble":"194111"},{"date":"16:52 09/08","title":"2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Ligue 1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/3/15/2-doi-bong-o-ligue-1-dai-chien-vi-rakitic.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ligue 1 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n mua Rakitic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPSG \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ef1c m\u1ea1nh, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. Trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p duy nh\u1ea5t Verratti l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u1edf \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p cao, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/15/2-doi-bong-o-ligue-1-dai-chien-vi-rakitic.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>PSG v\u00e0 Monaco mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Rakitic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean c\u00e1c Ho\u00e0ng t\u1eed mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ivan Rakitic c\u1ee7a Barca, ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMonaco c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Rakitic, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ligue 1 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i PSG v\u00e0 Monaco th\u00ec <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-muon-nang-cap-tuyen-giua-bang-sao-khung-cua-barca-172-182166.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n mua Rakitic</span>, Mourinho nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco c\u00f3 Rakitic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mundo Deportivo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u1eef Ivan Rakitic b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i sau khi \u0111\u00e3 chia tay Iniesta.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ivan Rakitic cua Barcelona\" title=\"Ivan Rakitic cua Barcelona\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/11/liverpool-tranh-ivan-rakitic-voi-mu-trong-mua-he-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco s\u1edf h\u1eefu Ivan Rakitic r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng 125 tri\u1ec7u euro, c\u00e1ch duy nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 chi \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1edfi Monaco kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh qu\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh, c\u00f2n v\u1edbi PSG n\u1ebfu ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua Rakitic r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd s\u1ebd vi ph\u1ea1m Lu\u1eadt c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u1eefa v\u1edbi hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf Ligue 1 l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Rakitic c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Barca. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Monaco v\u00e0 PSG chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Rakitic l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5289","checkdouble":"194119"},{"date":"16:29 09/08","title":"Mateo Kovacic CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ra m\u1eaft Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/mateo-kovacic-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-chelsea.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kovacic ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u00e1ng nay, ph\u00eda Real Madrid th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec7c chi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/mateo-kovacic-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-chelsea.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mateo Kovacic ra m\u1eaft Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, trong h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t. D\u00f9 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t hay d\u1edf th\u00ec \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1eabn quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Bernabeu.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n, anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mateo Kovacic t\u1edbi Chelsea</span> ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Chelsea, anh s\u1ebd gi\u00fap HLV Sarri c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kovacic n\u00f3i g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Chelsea?</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong ng\u00e0y ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kovacic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac v\u00e0 h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 n\u00e0y\u201d.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic\" title=\"Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chelsea-chieu-mo-kovacic-bai-toan-kho-danh-cho-sarri.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kovacic r\u1ea5t vui khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNgo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t, nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i t\u00f4i ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng HLV v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap t\u00f4i nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Marina Granovskaia c\u1ee7a Chelsea th\u00ec kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Kovacic, ch\u00e0o m\u1eebng c\u1eadu \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Chelsea, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Sarri x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Kovacic s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5288","checkdouble":"194117"},{"date":"16:17 09/08","title":"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kovacic: HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chelsea-chieu-mo-kovacic-bai-toan-kho-danh-cho-sarri.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic t\u1eeb Real Madrid. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng gi\u00fap anh ph\u00e1t huy t\u1ed1i \u0111a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Inter \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Kovacic khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y m\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i. H\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Dinamo Zagreb. Nh\u01b0ng Inter \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i b\u1edfi Kovacic t\u1eebng t\u1eadp th\u1eed \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y khi c\u00f2n l\u00e0 c\u1eadu b\u00e9 10 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00f3t v\u00e0o tai Kovacic. \u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Javier Zanetti kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh l\u00e0 sao tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Ro \u201cb\u00e9o\u201d l\u00e0m m\u01b0a l\u00e0m gi\u00f3 n\u0103m 1997.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u0129 nhi\u00ean, thi \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi Kovacic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao ngay cho chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 10. Anh kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Walter Mazzarri m\u00f9a 2013/14 v\u00e0 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u00e0 bao khi Roberto Mancini c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn. C\u00e1c HLV n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u hy v\u1ecdng Kovacic ch\u01a1i \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng trao m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kovacic HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Kovacic HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 gi\u1ea3i h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Chelsea-chieu-mo-Kovacic-HLV-Sarri-doi-dien-bai-toan-kho-giai-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kovacic t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Pirlo khi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Inter</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau c\u00f9ng, Kovacic b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y t\u1edbi Real Madrid n\u0103m 2015 ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y sau khi Zanetti kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin tr\u1ecdn v\u1eb9n v\u00e0o anh. Th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Samir Handanovic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Kovacic \u201cc\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d. V\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 c\u00e1c HLV ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho Kovacic.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede Italia, Kovacic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng trong vai tr\u00f2 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft l\u00f9i s\u00e2u. Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t Andrea Pirlo m\u1edbi nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169ng ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Giovanni Trapattoni mi\u00eau t\u1ea3 Kovacic l\u00e0 \u201cs\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p gi\u1eefa Kaka v\u00e0 Seedorf\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u1ea3 th\u1eadt, Kovacic c\u00f3 b\u1ed9 k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng. Anh r\u00ea b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec7u ngh\u1ec7 nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i th\u00edch ch\u01a1i l\u00f9i s\u00e2u. Anh kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef9 n\u0103ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eeba \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1ecf neo v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 10.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAndrea Stramaccioni, HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Kovacic t\u1ea1i Inter kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cKovacic kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i trong vai tr\u00f2 s\u1ed1 10 nh\u01b0 khi c\u00f2n nh\u1ecf\u201d. C\u00f2n Rafa Benitez c\u0169ng t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0a m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t khi\u1ebfn t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 m\u00f4ng lung: \u201cKovacic kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t\u201d. V\u00e0 th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea trong 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Kovacic t\u1ea1i Real cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng trong l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic\" title=\"Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/161159-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kovacic ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKovacic x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 4 t\u1ea1i La Liga v\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 r\u00ea b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong 90 ph\u00fat m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Anh c\u0169ng x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 9 v\u1ec1 t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n m\u1ed7i 90 ph\u00fat v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 14 v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 pha t\u1eafc b\u00f3ng. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong top 25 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 3 ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Mateo Kovacic</span> b\u1ecb gi\u1edbi h\u1ea1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. 11 trong s\u1ed1 21 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. T\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng, Kovacic c\u00f3 109 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Real Madrid v\u00e0 k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u1ea3 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u v\u1edbi ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o trong c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3. H\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, Kovacic c\u0169ng ra s\u00e2n 5 trong 7 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Croatia nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i 24, Kovacic c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf m\u00ecnh. Pirlo c\u0169ng t\u1eebng m\u1ea5t r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 th\u0103ng hoa khi c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e2y quanh anh. Nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Real Madrid l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho Kovacic. Chelsea ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh b\u1ed5 tr\u1ee3 cho Kovacic khi ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u01b0\u1ee3n anh v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic\" title=\"Kovacic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/161353-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sarri \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e0i to\u00e1n kh\u00f3 sau khi c\u00f3 Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft l\u00e0 Jorginho. C\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 con thoi c\u1ee7a Kante. Chelsea c\u0169ng c\u00f3 trong tay nh\u1eefng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o kh\u00e1c \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn tr\u00ean. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, Kovacic c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u01b0u \u0111i\u1ec3m gi\u00fap Kovacic c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ec9 ra s\u00e2n l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a Kovacic c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 HLV Sarri b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ra m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed m\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u1ec9 khi \u0111\u00f3, Kovacic m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n t\u1ea1o ra nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi thay v\u00ec b\u1ecb coi l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u201ck\u00e9p ph\u1ee5\u201d h\u1ea1ng sang nh\u01b0 b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-chelsea-niu-keo-hazard-o-lai-sau-khi-mat-courtois-172-194106.html\">Sao Chelsea n\u00edu k\u00e9o Hazard \u1edf l\u1ea1i sau khi m\u1ea5t Courtois</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/giai-ma-kepa-arrizabalaga-tan-binh-71-trieu-bang-cua-chelsea-172-194099.html\">Gi\u1ea3i m\u00e3 Kepa Arrizabalaga \u2013 T\u00e2n binh 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/day-top-10-thu-mon-dat-gia-nhat-the-gioi-184-194091.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! Top 10 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5287","checkdouble":"194118"},{"date":"17:07 09/08","title":"Mourinho bi quan v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/mourinho-bi-quan-ve-kha-nang-mua-them-nguoi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo b\u00e0i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, HLV Jose Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m tr\u1ea1ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vui v\u1ebb cho l\u1eafm.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nM.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Premier League ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n v\u00e0i ti\u1ebfng n\u1eefa l\u00e0 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn d\u1eadm ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7 v\u1edbi 3 t\u00e2n binh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3. Mourinho r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c khi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i qu\u00e1 ch\u1eadm tr\u1ec5 tr\u00ean th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: &ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 tin l\u1eafm. TTCN s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay, v\u00ec v\u1eady gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac t\u00f4i ng\u1eebng suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 n\u00f3. Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin t\u00f4i c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, M.U s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00ecnh \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu, chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 trong 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Sau \u0111\u00f3, c\u00e1c \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia s\u1ebd h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u1ea3 d\u0129 nh\u1ea5t \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n n\u00e0y.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" title=\"Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/mourinho-bi-quan-ve-kha-nang-mua-them-nguoi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ea3i qua World Cup \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u00edt ng\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp, v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u. T\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 s\u1ebd n\u00f3i v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i, r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o. S\u1ef1 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u trong to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;Trong b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c, v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, \u0111i\u1ec1u ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;\u1ede m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ecdc \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u01b0\u1edbi M.U \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 tin. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 8 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch v\u00e0 3 Premier League, nh\u01b0ng nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00e1c C\u0110V Man United \u0111ang r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Toby Alderweireld.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-scholes-du-doan-mu-nup-bong-man-city-mourinho-ra-duong-172-194105.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/8/paul-scholes-du-doan-mu-nup-bong-man-city-mourinho-ra-duong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-scholes-du-doan-mu-nup-bong-man-city-mourinho-ra-duong-172-194105.html\">Paul Scholes d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n: MU n\u00fap b\u00f3ng Man City, Mourinho ra \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng</span><br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea1c quan v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng Old Trafford.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wayne-rooney-mu-chi-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-neu-172-194089.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/7/9/wayne-rooney-mu-chi-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-neu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/wayne-rooney-mu-chi-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-neu-172-194089.html\">Wayne Rooney: MU ch\u1ec9 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19 n\u1ebfu...</span><br>\r\nWayne Rooney ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5286","checkdouble":"194120"},{"date":"17:13 09/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \"bom x\u1ecbt\" c\u1ee7a Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-west-ham-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>West Ham mua Lucas Perez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham quan t\u00e2m Lucas Perez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/ban-hop-dong-thu-9-cua-west-ham-den-tu-arsenal-172-193962.html\" target=\"_blank\">West Ham quan t\u00e2m Lucas Perez</span> c\u1ee7a Arsenal. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C West Ham mua Lucas Perez t\u1eeb Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C West Ham mua Lucas Perez t\u1eeb Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/4/CHINH-THUC-West-Ham-mua-Lucas-Perez-tu-Arsenal-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>West Ham quan t\u00e2m Lucas Perez\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Deportivo de La Coruna theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, anh ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 5 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, song kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu trong tay Lacazette, Aubameyang v\u00e0 Welbeck, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i West Ham th\u00ec Sporting Lisbon c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha, song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5\u00a0n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>West Ham ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Perez</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham mua Lucas Perez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 29 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 8 c\u1ee7a West Ham \u1edf H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, sau Ryan Fredericks, Lukasz Fabianski, Issa Diop, Jack Wilshere, Aindriy Yarmolenko, Fabian Balbuena v\u00e0 Felipe Anderson.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng bom x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng bom x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Arsenal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-west-ham-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>West Ham mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Perez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng song theo Sky Sport \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Perez West Ham \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i chi ra 8 tri\u1ec7u euro. Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi West Ham ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn West Ham, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed l\u00e2u \u0111\u1eddi. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ph\u1ea5n kh\u00edch khi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi West Ham\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cWest Ham c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, b\u1edfi v\u1eady, t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t h\u00e0o h\u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n v\u00e0 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Mario Husillos ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Perez \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham: \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n Lucas \u0111\u1ebfn West Ham United, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t \u0111a n\u0103ng, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n trong k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a West Ham \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5285","checkdouble":"194121"},{"date":"17:39 09/08","title":"MU v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Leicester","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/6/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-mu-mua-giai-201718.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M.U v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n NHA 2018/19</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Bayern Munich, M.U \u0111ang t\u00edch c\u1ef1c chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester, Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester, Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/Truoc-tran-gap-Leicester,-Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Matic v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i cho nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNemanja Matic, Sergio Romero, Marcos Rojo, Antonio Valencia, Diogo Dalot v\u00e0 Ander Herrera s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Leicester. Matic, Romero v\u00e0 Dalot ph\u1ea3i ph\u1eabu thu\u1eadt ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, Rojo g\u1eb7p v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf World Cup 2018, Herrera v\u00e0 Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf lo\u1ea1t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu H\u00e8 2018\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cThi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t khi\u1ebfn M.U g\u1eb7p kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, nh\u01b0ng trong tay t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Leicester, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho bi quan v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a M.U</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, M.U m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 chi ra 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Fred, Datlot v\u00e0 Lee Grant, Mourinho mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u HLV Chelsea b\u1ecf ra bi quan v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c BL\u0110 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng y\u00eau c\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nghich ly cua Jose Mourinho la luon tu tao ra dinh kien nhung lai nua muon thua nhan, nua khong.\" title=\"Ngh\u1ecbch l\u00fd c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho l\u00e0 lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u1ecbnh ki\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng l\u1ea1i n\u1eeda mu\u1ed1n th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn, n\u1eeda kh\u00f4ng.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/mourinho-xac-nhan-mu-vang-6-cau-thu-o-tran-gap-leicester-vi-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho bi quan v\u1ec1 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u00ean BL\u0110. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, nh\u01b0ng g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. BL\u0110 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00f4i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i m\u00e0 th\u00f4i, b\u1edfi t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 \u0111ang c\u00f3 trong tay\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wayne-rooney-mu-chi-vo-dich-ngoai-hang-anh-201819-neu-172-194089.html\" target=\"_blank\">Rooney n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 MU</span>, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 2 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5284","checkdouble":"194123"},{"date":"11:02 09/08","title":"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Roma treo th\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1eb1ng si\u00eau xe Lamborghini","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chu-tich-roma-treo-thuong-bang-sieu-xe-lamborghini.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5283","checkdouble":"194092"}]}